name: Ratna Mangali
description:
Ratna Mangali, is the wife of Mpu Bahula and the son of Ni Calonarang, as written in Serat Calonarang page 17a,

From the marriage of Mpu Bahula and Ratna Manggali the following great figures were born: The eldest child of Ratna Manggali. A famous bachelor of Javanese literature.
